Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:01:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.77,0:00:05.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.56,0:00:13.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.49,0:00:33.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.46,0:00:36.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sound resonates\NInto my heart, so hard and deep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:40.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A field of stars spans endlessly\NAnd through it I carve a passageway
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.32,0:00:42.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In step with time as generations change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.19,0:00:44.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes and listen closely
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.19,0:00:47.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shooting stars stream on silently…\Nuntil the goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:50.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the light inside of you,\Nnever give up don't ever lose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:52.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Transcend time and you will prove,\Nthere is a special place for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.09,0:00:53.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A blaze of glory is there,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:00:56.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all a part of our estate;\Nlife is our story to create
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.97,0:01:01.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.64,0:01:05.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old by voice of light\NThroughout the age, never fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:09.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A secret fire, a scream of light,\Nvoices calling through twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:11.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cast your thoughts to the wind,\Nhang your wishes on the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.22,0:01:13.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Live your life with all your strength\Nfor dreams will reach you very soon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.44,0:01:16.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:19.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old\Nby voice of light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.07,0:01:21.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Throughout the age,\Nnever fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.16,0:01:24.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Someday your dream will find\Nits place somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.05,0:01:28.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep shining like a star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.16,0:01:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.65,0:01:34.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.82,0:01:36.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,For this week's\N"Burarei"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.46,0:01:41.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,we're broadcasting live from\Nan abandoned hospital in Karakura
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.19,0:01:44.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,where ghostly screams are heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.49,0:01:49.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What will we witness tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.74,0:01:53.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And now,\Nlet us welcome him to the stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.45,0:01:55.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The charismatic medium of\Nthis new century...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.28,0:01:58.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The messenger from the Underworld...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.53,0:02:03.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mister...Don...Kan'onji!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.00,0:02:10.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Spirits…are always…\Nwith you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.19,0:02:15.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Live Broadcast of\NSpecial Program
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.79,0:02:18.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Checking Out Spiritual Hot Spots:\NGhostly Screams in an Abandoned Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:22.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bohahahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:27.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? There's almost no reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.32,0:02:29.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you\Nknow what this means?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.19,0:02:31.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,B-Burarei...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.19,0:02:34.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Correct! Isn't it a fun show?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.07,0:02:36.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Ichigo, can you join...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.15,0:02:38.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Bohaha--\N– Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:42.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tatsuki! What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.33,0:02:45.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, I'll join you on\Nthe "Bohaha" thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.75,0:02:46.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why…?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.20,0:02:49.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yo! Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.55,0:02:51.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Asano here.\N– And Mizuiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.05,0:02:54.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bohahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:57.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not going?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:02:59.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's the best Japanese TV\Nprogram on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:03.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And it's coming to Karakura Town for\Na live broadcast!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:07.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You'd have to be dead to be\Na citizen of this town and not go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:08.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm a zombie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:10.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Big deal. Now, get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.90,0:03:13.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I even asked Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:16.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hello Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:20.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Rukia... Bohahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.19,0:03:23.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no... I'm too embarrassed to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.95,0:03:25.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh come on, Rukia. Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:26.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.78,0:03:29.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She's adding to her repertoire\Nof tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:32.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kan'onji!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.22,0:03:34.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He’s so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.26,0:03:36.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How are you all?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.10,0:03:41.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you babies listen to\Nthe cries of the spirits tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:44.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Mr. Kan'onji?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.19,0:03:46.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:50.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This place reeks with\Nthe smell of spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.99,0:03:52.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This really...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.19,0:03:54.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Smells like bad spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.81,0:03:57.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bohahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:03:59.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bohahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.28,0:04:06.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cut to commercial!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.90,0:04:11.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I hate shows about spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.24,0:04:18.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please follow the guide to\Nthe spirit purification hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.99,0:04:19.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.99,0:04:20.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:22.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Umm… I'm sorry about the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:23.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.19,0:04:28.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuki said that you don't like these kinds\Nof programs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:30.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:32.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.\NI don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:33.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bohahahahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:35.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look at those guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:37.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,even though they know\NI hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.11,0:04:40.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But you still came.\NWhy is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.19,0:04:45.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My dad and sister are\Nbig fans of this show.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:47.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why you came?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.36,0:04:50.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I guess. Couldn't just let them come alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:54.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're very kind, Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:55.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Isn't it normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:05:00.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh, you're right. It's normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:02.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:07.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Orihime!\NWe're leaving you behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.65,0:05:10.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuki, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.57,0:05:19.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...all these people!\NAll caught up in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:21.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:24.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bohahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.70,0:05:25.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:29.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now now, what's that serious look for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.19,0:05:32.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take advantage of this and enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.78,0:05:34.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, I'm always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.24,0:05:39.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You must be exhausted from school\Nand Soul Reaper work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:42.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There will be hard battles ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:45.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Use this opportunity to spread your wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:47.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia, you…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:50.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:52.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,just what is this festival about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:54.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You came along without knowing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.19,0:06:01.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, are there really spirits in an\Nabandoned hospital like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.49,0:06:02.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.99,0:06:04.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If there were,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.12,0:06:06.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,wouldn't you Soul Reapers\Nhave helped it cross over?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:08.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not necessarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.86,0:06:10.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Spirits that inhabit a place\Nlike this
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.19,0:06:11.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,are usually Fixed-location\Njibaku spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:15.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Since these spirits assimilate\Ninto the earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.16,0:06:18.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,they're rarely detected by\Nthe Soul Society or Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:21.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There is only one condition
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.92,0:06:23.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,under which Fixed-location\Njibaku spirits show themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.20,0:06:27.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When humans invade their territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:35.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Chad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:36.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hear something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.19,0:06:37.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.19,0:06:41.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,C-Cut it out, Chad.\NYou're giving me the creeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.49,0:06:42.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's just your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:47.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe... Sorry, I'm just imagining it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.49,0:06:51.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have come, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.36,0:06:53.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's wrong, Karin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.65,0:06:54.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:01.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's the cry of\Na Fixed-location jibaku spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.36,0:07:02.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems there is one, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.70,0:07:06.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a Hollow's cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.45,0:07:11.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're aware that the occurrence of\NHollows follows several patterns.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:15.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One is when\Na Fixed-location jibaku spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:18.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,who feels a strong attachment\Nto this world is left alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.19,0:07:20.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and ends up becoming a Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:21.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Such as this spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:23.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then he’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:26.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,called a Plus, one on the verge of\Nbecoming a Hollow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.16,0:07:27.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,a Demi-Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:34.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He feels like a Hollow to me,\Nthat's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:37.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But he's not wearing that white mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.32,0:07:41.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Also, the hole in his chest\Nisn't fully opened yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.20,0:07:45.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The hole in a Hollow's chest\Nsignifies that the heart is lost
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.08,0:07:47.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and has become a mass\Nof simple instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.24,0:07:53.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The skull-shaped white mask shields\Nthe bared instincts from the outside world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.36,0:07:57.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Neither of these is necessary\Nif the heart is still intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.40,0:07:59.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When a human dies,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:01.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the chain of fate is\Nsevered from the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.19,0:08:04.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Usually the spirit\Nwaits for a Soul Reaper to guide it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:06.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but if they have regrets and\Ncannot let go,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:09.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,their chains become bound to\Nthe object of their regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:19.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This Demi-Hollow's heart\Nis being held by the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:22.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This hospital is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:24.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone\Nhave it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.21,0:08:26.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You guys better not come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:28.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to become a rich man here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:30.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– And I'm gonna ride a pink Cadillac,\N– What a disgusting spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.62,0:08:32.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– and drink pink Dom Perignon!\N– Coming back from commercial!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:35.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Something's about to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.19,0:08:42.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Spirits are always with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.19,0:08:46.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Bohahaha!\N– Bohahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:47.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is this okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:49.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.07,0:08:52.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It usually takes several\Nmonths to become a Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.03,0:08:54.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, the time has come
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.42,0:08:57.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,for Mr. Kan'onji's purification\Nof the spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:09:00.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want the spirit\Nto become agitated
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.19,0:09:01.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,with this many people around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.32,0:09:04.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We can do the Konso after\Nthe festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.65,0:09:05.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.32,0:09:09.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There is a frightening scream\Njust before one becomes a Hollow,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:11.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,it will be in much pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:14.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Does that Demi-Hollow look to be\Nsuffering to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:16.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:20.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to taint\Nmy hospital, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:22.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You've got guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:23.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that weird hat!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.19,0:09:25.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't look like it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:26.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:30.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Unless the partially closed hole in\Nhis chest is damaged in some way,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.19,0:09:33.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,it'll take another half\Na year to become a Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:40.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you cross\Nover peacefully, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:42.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ohhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.03,0:09:45.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There it is! The Super Spirit Cane!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:48.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,For him to use it at\Nthis early stage is truly unusual!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.61,0:09:50.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's he doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.49,0:09:51.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.60,0:09:55.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It will only speed up the process\Nof becoming a Hollow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:10:00.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!\NKiru-kiru-au-nan, au-maku-kiru-nan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.15,0:10:05.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:07.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's that guy doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.82,0:10:09.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Security! Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:14.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This way! Transform into a Soul Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.70,0:10:15.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:17.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:24.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.19,0:10:27.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:34.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who did that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:36.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hello…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:38.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Geta clogs and hat dude?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:40.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just sit there.\NHurry and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.19,0:10:42.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:44.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.19,0:10:45.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.99,0:10:46.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:49.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Move, leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.36,0:10:49.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.99,0:10:51.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:52.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.19,0:10:58.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kan'onji is flying\Nthrough the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:11:00.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's with you, boy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.90,0:11:02.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.86,0:11:03.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.69,0:11:06.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the charismatic medium of\Nthis new century!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.19,0:11:10.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see! You're dead,\Nand you're a fan, huh, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:12.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna get it, punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:22.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me I'm too late?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.36,0:11:50.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He disappeared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:55.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Mission complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.99,0:11:57.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– No way!\N– The soul purification is complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.30,0:11:58.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.23,0:12:02.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In the instant a Demi-Hollow turns\Ninto a Hollow,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.71,0:12:06.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,it disperses then reforms\Nin another location.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:10.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, if his heart was held\Nby this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.86,0:12:17.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kan'onji! Kan'onji! Kan'onji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.19,0:12:20.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:22.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Above you, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:23.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:55.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.28,0:12:57.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's called a Hollow, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:12:58.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:00.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I feel it, I feel it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:04.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It reeks of a super\Ndangerous spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:05.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.71,0:13:09.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You must be the evil boss come to\Navenge that soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:11.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.19,0:13:15.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,T-The pain... Let me eat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:18.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Hold it!\N– Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.41,0:13:20.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Run, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:26.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, bad spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:29.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don Kan'onji, the charismatic medium\Nof the new century, will take you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.65,0:13:31.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll devour you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:33.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:41.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you run away, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:43.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who\Nshould run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:47.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Run?! What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:51.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.19,0:13:55.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:56.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.49,0:13:58.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Although the conditions\Nare the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.28,0:14:00.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So, what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.19,0:14:11.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Golden chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:13.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:18.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:21.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Mr. Kan'onji did some unusual moves...\N– I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:24.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– then went into the building!\N– So that's how you're going to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.73,0:14:28.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The glass at the entrance is shattered,\Nand the walls are destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.87,0:14:34.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kan'onji must be battling\Nwith some unknown force!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.02,0:14:35.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.21,0:14:39.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Hollow of that level won't\Nbe a problem for Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.12,0:14:40.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:43.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's not good to create\Ntoo much of a fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:47.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Kan'onji seems to have\Na bit of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.23,0:14:49.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's let them handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:53.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why are we running away, boy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:56.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who said to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:58.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I meant only for you to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.95,0:15:00.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:01.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.12,0:15:10.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I run while you stay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.78,0:15:11.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Explain that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.36,0:15:13.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.53,0:15:16.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.73,0:15:19.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I am the hero, that's why!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:20.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:25.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you aware of the ratings\Nthat my show pulls in?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:27.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna bother answering.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.71,0:15:30.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Correct! 25%.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.19,0:15:34.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One in every four citizens\Nwatches my show.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:39.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And many of those viewers...\Nare children!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:44.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The children watch my every move\Nand become inspired.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.45,0:15:49.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They see me stand up to evil spirits and\Nunderstand what courage is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.36,0:15:51.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.57,0:15:56.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot run away\Nwhen these children are watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.19,0:15:59.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kan'onji...you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.28,0:16:03.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's go back and\Nfight that monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:04.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:07.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.99,0:16:09.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What if the audience gets involved?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:13.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That spirit is going after people with\Nhigh spiritual energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.92,0:16:15.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,like you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.45,0:16:18.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Without a doubt,\Nit's gonna come after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.19,0:16:20.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And if we fight here,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:22.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,at least no one in the\Naudience will get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.82,0:16:25.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:27.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.45,0:16:32.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You've thought it through\Nthat far?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:35.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Boy!\N– Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.07,0:16:38.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:42.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let me eat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:44.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:50.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not enough room!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:55.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! This room is too small\Nto use my Zanpaku-to!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.03,0:16:59.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.82,0:17:00.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:05.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I can't get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:07.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:08.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Arghh! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:32.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, boy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.66,0:17:34.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He came again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:37.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.19,0:17:39.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Run! Kan'onji!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.90,0:17:43.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.61,0:17:45.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.19,0:17:57.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kan'onji…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.02,0:17:59.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:01.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Get outta here!\NYou can't handle him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.42,0:18:02.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.29,0:18:03.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.19,0:18:05.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know my power,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.19,0:18:08.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and I know the difference in power\Nbetween the enemy and myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:11.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I have been impressed by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:15.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You put the safety of others first.\NGreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.64,0:18:19.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are my comrade,\Nlet me call you "friend."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:23.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Err...that's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.82,0:18:28.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Arghh! Kan’onji Style\NUltimate Technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.19,0:18:30.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cannon Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.37,0:18:49.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kan'onji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.28,0:18:52.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even if this body is blown apart,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.78,0:18:56.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,if I can die as a shield\Nfor the kids of the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:59.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I shall have no regrets in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:02.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.03,0:19:06.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.78,0:19:12.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but this is the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.77,0:19:17.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.44,0:19:26.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Great! Magnificent! Magnificent!\NMagnifi--!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.54,0:19:27.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kan’onji.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.11,0:19:30.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get too excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.61,0:19:35.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why, boy?\NYou defeated the monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:37.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You should rejoice! Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:40.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.63,0:19:46.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No way! He's the one who...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.19,0:19:48.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.57,0:19:50.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's a Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.19,0:19:53.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When the chain that links\Nhis soul is broken and
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:54.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,a hole opens up in his chest,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.99,0:19:58.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the spirit becomes a monster without\Nconscience, a Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.61,0:20:01.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chest? Hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:03.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:08.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What have I been doing\Nall this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.99,0:20:15.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I am ashamed of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:26.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, quit crying, Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.65,0:20:29.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.19,0:20:42.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.25,0:20:43.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Answer their cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.24,0:20:46.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's a hero's duty, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.19,0:20:48.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.66,0:20:53.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Mr. Kan'onji's soul purification\Nseems to be over!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:57.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mission Complete! Bohahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:21:01.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bohahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:05.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Kan'onji!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:10.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, that was a magnificent battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.15,0:21:15.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I admire your courage and power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.24,0:21:18.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lend me your strength from now on, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:23.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well...once in a while, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:27.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.99,0:21:29.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,From today, you are…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.07,0:21:31.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,my number one pupil!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:34.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's a demotion!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.23,0:22:03.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Though the voyage must continue on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.49,0:22:08.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,May seas always be calm
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.65,0:22:13.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When the cycle of the moon\Nhas renewed may it shine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.71,0:22:18.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's light to guide your boat
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.97,0:22:23.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I offer this voyage a prayer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.40,0:22:28.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With each new day that still awaits
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.35,0:22:32.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,On vividly shining seas
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.74,0:22:39.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the end of the journey
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.71,0:22:43.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia and I headed out to\Nexterminate Hollows,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.19,0:22:45.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– but someone beat us to it.\N– Bohahaha! I'm Don Kan'onji!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.23,0:22:46.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now everyone repeat after me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.71,0:22:49.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– A mysterious figure watches us...\N– Bohahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.50,0:22:50.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.79,0:22:52.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Shut up, will you?!\N– One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.25,0:22:54.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Please, go home, I'm begging you!\N– Bohahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.70,0:22:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,